Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,後面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,空 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙是木氣的靈災 不好意思借我用一用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,火勢比預想要大…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去要…
