Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,火的咒術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,偏偏是那傢伙的
